--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 Key
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
A - Added
R - Removed
F - Fixed
K - Known issue

0.5		2013/07/19	(Ib 1.5a1pre - 1.5)
R   Dropped Ib < 1.5 support to be compatible with the new tabs
F   Support for Ib 1.5
F   Updated License to MPL 2

0.4		2011/06/04	(Ib 0.3a3pre - 0.3b2pre)
R   Dropped Ib 0.2 support to be compatible with the new tabs
F   Support new Firefox 4.0 style tabs
K   Selected tab does not "connect" properly to the conversation

0.3		2010/07/22	(Ib 0.2 - 0.3a1pre)
F	2	Better Linux compatibility (scrollbuttons and max tab height)
F	5	Resizable / hidden tabs

0.2		2010/07/14	(Ib 0.2pre - 0.3a1pre)
F	6	Drag and Drop works with indicators
F		Fixed better support for Linux/Mac -- untested!

0.1		2010/07/05	(Ib 0.2b2 - 0.2pre)
A		Small UI tweaks for Windows (fix bottom borders, fix scroll arrows)
F	7	UI no longer shifts when adding a second tab
F 	8	Fix detaching tabs
	9	Scrolling works as expected
A		Initial support for Linux/Mac -- tabs are now the correct height
K	6	Drag and Drop doesn't work

0.1pre	2010/07/02	(Ib 0.2b2 - 0.2pre)
A 		Initial version working for Windows
K 	7	Deselected tab is two pixels too wide
K	8	Detaching tabs places tabs far away from window
